data.description: Take a look at this beautiful home in Dreamland Villa, the desirable 55+ community in Mesa. This 3 bedroom/2 bathroom house has just recently had luxury vinyl flooring put in, so now there is no carpet! The kitchen has updated espresso cabinets and corian countertops, and opens into the family room. The floorplan is split so the primary bedroom is separate from the other 2 bedrooms.  Enjoy a cup of coffee on the new furniture on the covered patio out front or in the large backyard. Dreamland Villa has an optional HOA if you would like to enjoy the amenities it has to offer! From community pools to numerous activities, it is truly a great neighborhood!
